<p><img src="/img/keepassxc/blank-add-new-entry.png" alt="Add new entry button" /></p>

<p>Weâ€™ll be presented with an interface to create our new entry. Letâ€™s fill in a title (Reddit), Username (our Reddit username), our Reddit password twice, and then the URL of the site (https://www.reddit.com), which you can of course paste in.</p>

<p><img src="/img/keepassxc/entry-creation.gif" alt="Our first entry" /></p>

<p>If you want to view your password, you can click the button with the eye icon on the right.</p>

<p>As mentioned, KeePassXC has the ability to generate random passwords for us, which we can do by clicking the black die icon. Weâ€™ll go over that below, but for now letâ€™s pretend weâ€™re simply storing your existing password that you hopefully know by heart (but wonâ€™t have to for much longer!).</p>

<p>Once weâ€™ve filled in this basic information, weâ€™ll click the OK button to create this new entry in our password database. Weâ€™ll now see our new entry in our database.</p>

